<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Several classes within {{Zend\Tool}} contain calls to {{\Zend\Filter\FilterChain::addFilter}} which has apparently been renamed {{\Zend\Filter\FilterChain::attach}}.</p>

<p>This causes {{zf.php}} to issue a fatal error.</p>

